{
  "id": "adv_card_rei_03_02",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜 2話 お願いだから引っ込んで",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――わんこそば早食い競争後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After the soba speed-eating contest",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "怜、遅いな、どこに行ったんだ？\nもうすぐ、次の――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei‚ you're late.\nWhere have you been?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.8666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6779.1608493,
          "startTime": 9.9124941826
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2900.0000000000014,
          "startTime": 10.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "あの、{user}さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah…{user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "怜、良かった。遅いから心配――\nん？　どうした？　元気がないみたいだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was worried since you're late――\nHuh? What's wrong? You seem down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……その……大変言い辛いんですけど\n…………着られないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… umm… it's difficult to say‚ but…\n…I can't fit into it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "え？　何を？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "この後、サニピのメンバー全員で\n新しい衣装を着て、ライブじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After this‚ all members of Sunny Peace are\nsupposed to wear new outfits for the live performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、それがこのフェスの目玉のイベントで……\nあっ、まさか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ that's the highlight of this festival…\nOh‚ don't tell me…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "…………はい、そのまさかです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes‚ exactly that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "食べ過ぎで、衣装が着られないっていうのか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You mean you can't wear it because you ate too much!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっ、そんなに大きな声で言わないで下さい！\n恥ずかしいじゃないですか……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ don't say it so loudly!\nIt's embarrassing‚ you know…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ごめん。でも年末からよく食べてたとはいえ\nカロリー計算は完璧だったんだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry. But even though you've been eating a lot since\nthe year-end‚ your calorie counting was perfect‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "……それが、さっき確認したらアプリの設定を\n間違ってたみたいで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Well‚ it seems I made a mistake\nin the app settings when I checked earlier…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "それに加えて、さっきのわんこそばのドカ食いで\nとどめを刺してしまいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And in addition‚ that contest\nearlier was the final blow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（……ツッコミどころが多過ぎて、何も言えない……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…There are too many things to point out‚ I can't say anything…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私、どうしたら……\nこのままだと、私だけステージに上がれません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-What am I supposed to do…\nIf it stays like this‚ I'll be the only one who can't go up on stage…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "なら、スタイリストさんに頼んで\n大急ぎで寸法を直してもらうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ why not ask the stylist to quickly fix the measurements…\n…Or is that a bad idea?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは嫌です！　みんなと並んだ時\n明らかに私だけ一回り大きく見えちゃいます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-No‚ I don't want that! When I stand with everyone else‚\nit will be obvious that I look much bigger!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "一ノ瀬怜、激太りとかネットニュースに書かれたら……\n私、耐えられません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If \"Rei Ichinose gains extreme weight\" ends up on the internet news…\nI won't be able to handle it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "いつものステージ衣装も入らないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can't you fit into your regular stage outfit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "あっちならギリギリなんとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can barely manage with that one…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、せっかく新しい衣装を用意してもらったのに\n着ない理由が食べ過ぎだなんて、とても言えません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ they prepared new outfits for me‚\nand to say that I can't wear them because I ate too much…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよな……一人だけ別の衣装だと悪目立ちするよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… if only one person wears a different outfit‚ it'll stand out too much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "日頃、みんなに自己管理は大事って言ってる私が\nこんなことになって……不様ですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As someone who always emphasizes the importance of self-management to everyone…\nIt's so embarrassing to end up like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "私のこと、笑って下さい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You can laugh at me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "……ライブまであと三時間……ギリギリいけるか\nよし、俺は腹をくくる。怜、今から俺は鬼になるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Three hours until the live performance… I think we can manage it.\nAlright‚ I'll toughen up. Rei‚ from now on‚ I'll become a demon.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
